data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! BEST DEAL IN ARLINGTON RIDGE! HOME WARRANTY! Recent refresh by the owner including NEW INTERIOR & EXTERIOR PAINT, and many NEW FIXTURES makes this one a MOVE-IN READY must-see home. Roof appears to be in good condition with no issues at all but due to the age, the seller will include a new roof with an acceptable offer if needed. Pick your color. Easy maintenance 2 bedroom, 2 bath home w/2 car garage & large, screened porch. All appliances are included w/natural gas stove, water heater, & central heat. Arlington Ridge is a Guard Gated Community featuring a Gorgeous 18 Hole Championship Golf Course (discounted for residents), Putting Green, Driving Range. The low HOA dues include Lawn Care, Fiber Optic Cable, and High-Speed Internet, Tennis & Pickle Ball Courts, Sidewalks for Jogging/Walking, the Chesapeake Grill and Tavern, Billiards Room, Movie Theater, Fairfax Hall, a state-of-the-art Fitness Center overlooking the Lap & Community Pools w/Beach & Hot Tub. There is also a separate Aerobics Room w/Showers, Lockers & Saunas in both & a huge Arts & Crafts room that handles multiple clubs & groups. Arlington Ridge is centrally located just a short drive from Florida's turnpike, 45 minutes from Orlando Airport, Theme Parks, and central to the beaches, both east and west coast. Minutes to the public boat ramp to the Harris Chain of Lakes, shopping, medical, and dining. Schedule a showing today!
